'''洪天照'''（{{lang-en|Sammy Hung}}，{{bd|1979年|11月15日|catIdx=H洪}}），香港[[演員|演員]]。他是導演[[洪金寶|洪金寶]]的第三個兒子<ref>{{cite news|title=洪天照被彭敬慈狂「撻」|url=http://paper.wenweipo.com/2018/02/14/EN1802140006.htm|accessdate=2021-09-03|work=香港文匯報|archive-date=2021-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210903054437/http://paper.wenweipo.com/2018/02/14/EN1802140006.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，演員[[洪天明|洪天明]]的第二名弟弟，港韓[[混血兒|混血兒]]，母為曹恩玉，後母[[高麗虹|高麗虹]]<ref>{{cite news |title=洪金寶37歲掌上明珠至今未嫁 3關鍵原因曝「和爸爸太像」 |url=https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201128003733-260404?chdtv |accessdate=2021-09-03 |work=中時新聞網 |language=zh-TW |archive-date=2021-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210903054414/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201128003733-260404?chdtv |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=開電影工作室 洪天明求洪金寶片酬打折 |url=https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170125/bkn-20170125150639354-0125_00862_001.html |accessdate=2021-09-03 |work=on.cc東網 |date=2017-01-25 |language=zh-hk |archive-date=2021-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210903025043/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170125/bkn-20170125150639354-0125_00862_001.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

